    "rationale": "Overall credibility is sufficient for the medium model risk level and medium decision consequence. Twelve of thirteen V&V 40 factors meet or exceed required levels. The single gap in Test conditions (achieved 2, required 3) is accepted given the standardized ASTM F1717 protocol and regulatory precedent. E/uval < 1.96 for all QoIs confirms adequate model accuracy within the validated domain.",
